data.description: Located in the highly desired school district of Western Branch. This home has been Freshly painted throughout and offers a fabulous floor plan with an open concept boasting a 2 story foyer, formal living room, dinning room, family room, 1st and 2nd floor ensuites and so much more. Just imagine yourself relaxing on the huge screened in porch overlooking the large deck and beautiful tree lined back yard as you enjoy your BBQ's and outdoor entertainment! Call today for your tour!
